description:
I should have split this episode into two, but you get a super long one instead! Today we do a bunch of farm building projects; a squid farm, slime farm, cave spider farm, and froglight farm.

We set up my ender chest refilling stations and look into a new idea for a super simple multi item sorting array. Then we check out what Hermit Permits I got in the random drawing and do some permit trading.
